It's time for [56%](../tag/56) Roshen bar brought to me as a gift from Ukraine. The appearance is almost identical to the [Roshen Brut bar](../78-percent-brut-chocolate-from-roshen/). Inside, as expected, less cocoa, more sugar. The taste is good, smooth, there is no acidity, but sweet, as for me.
A little less sugar and it would be good, so far only [3 stars](../tag/3-stars).

