Toms bar with [77%](../tag/77) of cocoa. When I bought it in [Copenhagen](../tag/made-in-denmark), I really liked it. I even bought two additional bars of it. After I opened one of them, and that was after we cam back from [France](../tag/made-in-france) with a bag full of [Pralus](../tag/pralus) bars, I can only give it [4 stars](../tag/4-stars). 
Simple but nice and decent packaging. Quite pure strong chocolate taste. A bit bitter, very slightly acidic. But aftertaste is a bit rough. Not that pleasant. Still not bad in general.

